{"tid":820657,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普捷天奴高呼VAR摧毀足球　諷英人同為騙過球證慶祝","createTime":"2018-09-15T14:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T14:40:21.000Z","uid":201862,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4a85320580e745ace8a8d88ab714ee3dafe548","tid":820657,"uid":201862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"熱刺日前憑爭議性12碼逼和利物浦，賽後熱刺迪利阿里、拉美拿、哈利卡尼等人的「插水」行為飽受抨擊。熱刺主帥普捷天奴在迎戰紐波特郡賽前，再次為愛將辯護，聲言欺騙也是戰術，而且球證有時難免犯錯，暗示欺騙球證是比賽的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n普捷天奴更直言擔心足球在數年後變得僵硬，不再充滿激情，他解釋：「足球是充滿想像的運動，VAR（視像裁判）會令人專注這些小動作。20年前、30年前，大家都以為騙過球證而慶祝，不單止阿根廷，英格蘭亦是一樣。」普捷天奴更總結：「足球就是要欺騙你的對手。球證也是人，有時他們是對，有時他們是錯，我喜歡這樣的足球。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c384ae14344a7dc63ae927da0b2cb07326758e","tid":820657,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱狗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/images/D5vXqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2FD5vXqg&d=S0akONC3rN1kuGo3BMaDKoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=26aed1c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/images/D5vXqg</a>"},{"pid":"a1be1e387743ae556584f01a8a30ebac4408cfe9","tid":820657,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9909305f3de89fd57e50ae560efe68b1a1f3a3cf","tid":820657,"uid":103947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"如果有var頭先果球都幾大機會吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos